 OAP DaddyFreeze is of the opinion that the phrase “What God cannot do does not exist” is “dangerous.” Freeze stated this while reacting to the death of gospel artiste, Osinachi Nwachukwu. According to him, there are things God can do but will not do for anyone.  He stressed that the church should start encouraging divorce and remarriage under the right circumstances. Read what he wrote below:Recall media personality, Morayo Afolabi-Brown had asked some questions she was confused about regarding late Osinachi.
The OAP had taken to clergywoman, Funke Felix-Adejumo’s page to ask her to shed some light on some things.